Dear all,

This code is very alpha, and intended to be developed fast.

The aim of this code is to authenticate signed image lists 
to facilitate sharing of VM's across HTC sites for high 
energy physics.

The code may be come more usiversal.

Contributors.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Below is a list fo contributors. If you help in thsi project please add your
name.

Owen Synge : owen.synge@desy.de



How to verify.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

To get the DN and CA of your signature.

openssl smime -in your_signed.msg \
 -pk7out | openssl pkcs7 -print_certs

To Verfy the message agaisnt the CA certificate.

openssl smime -in your_signed.msg \
 -CAfile /etc/grid-security/certificates/dd4b34ea.0 \
 -verify 1> /dev/null 
